         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;[Nikon] to Zenon greeting. Bia is asking for the two rams' fleeces which you left behind for making yarn. Write to us therefore if they are to be given to her. For she said that she is in need of woollen yarn and is behindhand for that reason. And indeed I had written to you about this before. Farewell. Year 29, Pharmouthi 25.;;(Verso);;To Zenon.;(upside down, on the right) About fleeces(?).;;(Docket, 2nd hand) Nikon(?) about two fleeces, asking if they are to be given to Bia. (Received) year 29, Daisios 11.</ab>
         </div>
